#

Spicy Szechuan Beef Stir-Fry

$15.75
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

SoyPeanuts

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

Asian CuisineSpicyStir-Fry

Description

A fiery blend of tender beef, crisp vegetables, and bold Szechuan spices, perfect for those craving heat!

Ingredients

  • Beef sirloin: 1 lb, sliced thinly
  • Bell peppers: 1 cup, sliced
  • Broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • Szechuan peppercorns: 1 tsp, crushed
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, minced
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Chili paste: 2 tbsp
  • Cornstarch: 1 tbsp
  • Vegetable oil: 2 tbsp
  • Green onions: 2, chopped for garnish
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp, for garnish
